reviewText:
This program has done more for me this year than a lot of other programs
Here Brendon goes into dept on what it takes to be a high performer,
I am a marketer and been on high energy on a daily basis is, well... Kind of tiresome,
Enter high Performance Academy, the information I needed,
now shooting my videos is a little easier because I know what to focus on,
rehearsals for speeches, what to eat before the task, how to get things done, I mean how to GET 'EM DONE!!!! buy it you owe it to yourself, I could be watching from the fence but I rather be part of the action. Cheers!
